<body>
  <section class="payments-credits">
      <div class="container">
          <h2>Payments & Credits</h2>
          
          <div class="content">
              <p class="intro">We offer flexible payment options to suit different business needs. You can pay by credit card, via direct bank transfer to our German corporate account, or request alternative methods like stablecoins or Bitcoin if needed. For card payments, we'll automatically charge your account when additional credits are required, making the process seamless.</p>

              <h3>Credit Management Process</h3>
              <p>When you approach your monthly message limit, we'll send a notification to give you time to purchase additional credits if needed. If you're paying by card, the system will attempt to automatically charge for extra credits. For bank transfer or crypto payments, we expect payment as soon as possible to maintain service continuity.</p>

              <p>In cases where your account exceeds the message limit without a successful payment, we provide a grace period to prevent immediate service interruption. This period extends for up to 3 days or until you've used an additional 1,000 messages, whichever comes first. During this grace period, you'll receive regular reminders to settle the payment and avoid service suspension.</p>

              <p>You can proactively purchase extra credits at any time to ensure uninterrupted service. This is particularly useful for businesses with fluctuating message volumes or those anticipating increased usage.</p>

              <h3>Enterprise Solutions</h3>
              <p>For businesses processing over 100,000 messages per month, we offer customized enterprise pricing with additional volume discounts. While our standard Pro account already provides competitive rates with efficiency at scale, we can provide additional value for high-volume customers. Contact our team to discuss enterprise options tailored to your specific requirements.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

